## tool-search-xai: search_xai tool definition

### search_xai(query: str, model: str = "grok-4-1-fast-reasoning") â†’ str
Search the web and X/Twitter using xAI Grok's x_search tool. Returns an AI-synthesized answer
with citations from real-time web results.

Parameters:
  model: "grok-4-1-fast-reasoning" (default, fast) or "grok-4" (full reasoning)

Use search_xai when:
- You need real-time information from the web or X/Twitter.
- The query involves current events, social media trends, or recent news.
- search_ddgs or search_tavily did not return satisfactory results.
- The user explicitly asks to search X (Twitter) or social media.

Requires XAI_API_KEY.

This tool always requires human gate approval before it executes.
